- content_for :head do
  = stylesheet_link_tag    "challenge", :media => "all"
.content
.challenge_top
  .challenge_title_text
    Take the Challenge!
  .challenge_subtext
    Go for a walk, hike, run or ride in a whole new way.
  .challenge_subtext_date
    The 2012 Challenge runs from July 19 - September 30
%hr.challenge_hr/
.challenge_content
  .challenge_content_left
    %h3 Why Take The Challenge
    .why.doing
      .icon
      .text
        .header
          You want to try something new
        .description
          Whether itâ€™s taking the bus or starting on an unfamiliar trail, here is an opportunity to explore new places and discover new ways of getting there.
    .why.exploring
      .icon
      .text
        .header
          You want to get outside and get moving
        .description
          Short walks or epic bike rides are welcome on the Challenge. Over a million acres of Bay Area parks and trails await you regardless of your ability and interests.
    .why.friends
      .icon
      .text
        .header
          You want to talk to your friends
        .description
          If you're not driving, you can talk, text, email, or simply enjoy the view out the window. You also won't have to deal with parking or traffic.
  / challenge_content_left
  .challenge_content_right
    %h3 How it works
    %ol
      %li
        %a{:href => "#{new_user_session_path}"} Login
        or
        %a{:href => "#{new_user_registration_path}"} Register
      %li
        %a{:href => "/find"} Find a trip or trailhead to explore.
      %li Plan your adventure using transit, biking, walking or driving.
      %li Share your story by clicking the Add a Story button on the trip or trailhead page. Tell us when you went, how you got there, and what you did!
    Tips, stories, prizes and more can be found on the
    = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => "http://blog.transitandtrails.org"} Transit & Trails Blog
    .clearfix
  .clearfix
  #sponsors
    %h3 Sponsors
    %a{:href => "http://www.mtc.ca.gov"}
      %img.logo{:src => "/assets/challenge/logos/mtc.png"}/
    %a{:href => "http://www.parksconservancy.org"}
      %img.logo{:src => "/assets/challenge/logos/ggnpc.png"}/
    .clearfix
  #partners
    %h3 Partners
    %a{:href => "http://www.sparetheair.org"}
      %img.logo{:src => "/assets/challenge/logos/spare_the_air.png"}/
    %a{:href => "http://www.rei.com"}
      %img.logo{:src => "/assets/challenge/logos/REI.jpg"}/
    %a{:href => "http://transformca.org/"}
      %img.logo{:src => "/assets/challenge/logos/transform.png"}/
    .clearfix
  #interested
    %h4
      Interested in joining the Challenge as a Sponsor or Partner?
    %a{:href => "/media/challenge/challenge_sponsors_partners.pdf"} Click here for more information
    or
    = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => "mailto:annie@openspacecouncil.org"} email us
